:\"$1a:props:children:1:props:children:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check-big\",\"size\":22,\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Tech-stack consolidation:\"}],\" Reducing your software bloat from 5 tools down to 1 centralized system cuts operational costs by 22%.\"]}]]}]\n25:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$1a:props:children:1:props:children:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check-big\",\"size\":22,\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Tenant self-service:\"}],\"Empowering tenants with an app reduces inbound support calls by over 60%, freeing up your team's bandwidth.\"]}]]}]\n26:[\"$\",\"nav\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-mobile-toc\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Table of Contents\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"intro\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" active\",\"href\":\"#intro\",\"children\":\"1. The scaling dilemma in 2026\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"automation\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#automation\",\"children\":\"2. Embracing the automation mindset\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"self-service\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\"nested \",\"href\":\"#self-service\",\"children\":\"2.1 The power of tenant self-service\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"financial\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#financial\",\"children\":\"3. Automating financial reconciliation\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"case-study\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#case-study\",\"children\":\"4. Real-world case study\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"conclusion\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#conclusion\",\"children\":\"5. Conclusion & Next Steps\"}]}]]}]]}]\n27:[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-article-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"id\":\"intro\",\"children\":[\"The property management industry is currently facing a unique paradox. Demand for high-quality rental units is soaring across urban centers, portfolio sizes are increasing exponentially as institutional capital enters the market, yet finding and retaining skilled operational staff has literally never been more difficult. For mid-sized agencies looking to double their door count over the next 24 months, the traditional operational model of \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-highlight-text\",\"children\":\"\\\"add 50 doors, hire 1 manager\\\" is fundamentally and financially broken.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We have analyzed data from over 2,000 property management firms. The ones succeeding are not simply grinding harder; they are working smarter. So, how do top-tier firms manage to scale their operations by 200% while maintaining the exact same headcount? The secret lies entirely in workflow optimization, tech-stack consolidation, and an aggressive approach to eliminating manual data entry.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"automation\",\"children\":\"Embracing the automation mindset\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Scaling without hiring requires a fundamental shift in how your entire team views their daily tasks. A property manager should not be treated as a glorified data-entry clerk. Their true value to your business lies in relationship building, high-level dispute resolution, and asset optimization. Everything else must be systematically automated.\"}],[\"$\",\"blockquote\",null,{\"children\":\"\\\"If a specific operational task requires clicking the exact same buttons every single month - like generating standard rent invoices, calculating late fees, or dispatching a plumber for a leaky faucet - software should be doing it, not a human being. Your team is too valuable for repetitive clicking.\\\"\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Consider the standard rent collection cycle. Historically, this involved logging into a bank portal, cross-referencing paper bank statements, manually updating individual tenant ledgers, and sending manual emails to late payers. Today, unified systems handle this entirely in the background. Invoices are auto-generated 7 days before the first of the month, late fees are auto-applied precisely based on custom lease terms, and ledgers are synchronized with accounting software in real-time.\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"id\":\"self-service\",\"children\":\"The power of tenant self-service\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"One of the largest, yet most invisible, drains on a property team's time is inbound administrative communication. Questions like \\\"When is the plumber coming?\\\", \\\"How do I pay rent online?\\\", or \\\"Can I get a copy of my lease agreement?\\\" can consume up to 40% of a property manager's day.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"By implementing a robust, intuitive tenant portal, you effectively shift the administrative burden away from your staff and directly to the end-user. When tenants have a 24/7 mobile app where they can view their live ledger balance, submit categorized photos of maintenance issues, and download compliance documents instantly, inbound phone call volume drops dramatically.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Reduced call volume:\"}],\" Participating agencies report an average 60% drop in phone calls within 3 months of strict portal adoption.\"]}],\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\"]}],\"$L30\",\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\"]}]\n28:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-tags\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Topics:\"}],[[\"$\",\"a\",\"Scaling Portfolios\",{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"Scaling Portfolios\"}],[\"$\",\"a\",\"Automation\",{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"Automation\"}],[\"$\",\"a\",\"Financial Operations\",{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"Financial Operations\"}]]]}]\n29:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-author-bio\",\"id\":\"author-bio\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-author-photo\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Sarah Jenkins\",\"height\":144,\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=250&auto=format&fit=crop\",\"width\":144}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:props:children:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-badge-check\",\"size\":27}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Written by Sarah Jenkins\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Sarah is a Certified Property Manager with over 12 years of experience managing multi-family and commercial real estate portfolios across the US. She specializes in operational efficiency, prop-tech implementation, and scaling business models. She is a regular contributor to the National Real Estate Journal.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"LinkedIn\",\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"in\"}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Twitter\",\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"x\"}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"Website\",\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\",\"key\":\"1cjeqo\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\",\"key\":\"19qd67\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-link\",\"size\":18}]}]]}]]}]]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comments\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comments-head\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Discussions\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"3 Comments\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comment-form\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Join the conversation\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *\"}],[\"$\",\"form\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-form-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Name *\"}],[\"$\",\"input\",null,{\"required\":true,\"type\":\"text\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Email *\"}],[\"$\",\"input\",null,{\"required\":true,\"type\":\"email\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Comment *\"}],[\"$\",\"textarea\",null,{\"required\":true,\"rows\":5}]]}],[\"$\",\"button\",null,{\"type\":\"button\",\"children\":\"Post Comment\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comment-list\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comment\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Marcus Thompson\",\"height\":64,\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599566150163-29194dcaad36?q=80&w=150&auto=format&fit=crop\",\"width\":64}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h5\",null,{\"children\":\"Marcus Thompson\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Oct 13, 2026 at 9:24 am\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"This is a fantastic breakdown. We struggled heavily with headcount bloat last year until we finally migrated our maintenance pipeline to a digital portal. The phone literally stopped ringing off the hook within a week of rollout.\"}],[\"$\",\"button\",null,{\"type\":\"button\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M17 7 7 17\",\"key\":\"15tmo1\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M17 17H7V7\",\"key\":\"1org7z\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-arrow-down-left\",\"size\":16}],\"Reply\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comment blog-detail-comment-reply\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Sarah Jenkins\",\"height\":56,\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=150&auto=format&fit=crop\",\"width\":56}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h5\",null,{\"children\":[\"Sarah Jenkins\",[\"$\",\"b\",null,{\"children\":\"Author\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Oct 13, 2026 at 11:05 am\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Glad to hear it resonated, Marcus! Getting tenants to actually adopt the app is usually the hardest part, but once they do, the operational savings are massive as you have seen.\"}],[\"$\",\"button\",null,{\"type\":\"button\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2a:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-arrow-down-left\",\"size\":16}],\"Reply\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-comment last\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-initials\",\"children\":\"EL\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h5\",null,{\"children\":\"Elena Rodriguez\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Oct 14, 2026 at 2:15 pm\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"I am curious about the QuickBooks sync mentioned. Does the platform handle multi-entity accounting seamlessly? We manage portfolios for multiple LLCs and need strict ledger separation across the board.\"}],[\"$\",\"button\",null,{\"type\":\"button\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2a:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:1:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-arrow-down-left\",\"size\":16}],\"Reply\"]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"aside\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-sidebar\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-sticky\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-card-title\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M3 5h.01\",\"key\":\"18ugdj\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M3 12h.01\",\"key\":\"nlz23k\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M3 19h.01\",\"key\":\"noohij\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M8 5h13\",\"key\":\"1pao27\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M8 12h13\",\"key\":\"1za7za\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M8 19h13\",\"key\":\"m83p4d\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-list\",\"size\":21}],\"On this page\"]}],[\"$\",\"nav\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-toc\",\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"intro\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" active\",\"href\":\"#intro\",\"children\":\"1. The scaling dilemma in 2026\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"automation\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#automation\",\"children\":\"2. Embracing the automation mindset\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"self-service\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\"nested \",\"href\":\"#self-service\",\"children\":\"2.1 The power of tenant self-service\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"financial\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#financial\",\"children\":\"3. Automating financial reconciliation\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"case-study\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#case-study\",\"children\":\"4. Real-world case study\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"conclusion\",{\"children\":[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\" \",\"href\":\"#conclusion\",\"children\":\"5. Conclusion & Next Steps\"}]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-card-title\",\"children\":\"Related Articles\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-related\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Announcing our new native QuickBooks integration\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-related-image\",\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Thumbnail\",\"className\":\"blog-img-cover\",\"fill\":true,\"sizes\":\"80px\",\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554200876-56c2f25224fa?q=80&w=150&auto=format&fit=crop\"}]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"Announcing our new native QuickBooks integration\"}],[\"$\",\"small\",null,{\"children\":\"Sep 15, 2026\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"The future of smart building technology\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-related-image\",\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Thumbnail\",\"className\":\"blog-img-cover\",\"fill\":true,\"sizes\":\"80px\",\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&w=150&auto=format&fit=crop\"}]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"The future of smart building technology\"}],[\"$\",\"small\",null,{\"children\":\"Sep 28, 2026\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-newsletter\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-newsletter-orb top\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-newsletter-orb bottom\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-detail-newsletter-icon\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\",\"key\":\"132q7q\"}],[\"rect\",{\"x\":\"2\",\"y\":\"4\",\"width\":\"20\",\"height\":\"16\",\"rx\":\"2\",\"key\":\"izxlao\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-mail\",\"size\":26}]}],[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"children\":\"Property Insights\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Get the latest scaling tips and feature updates delivered to your inbox weekly.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L3c\",null,{\"buttonLabel\":\"Subscribe Now\",\"source\":\"blog article sidebar newsletter\"}]]}]]}]}]\n2e:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Faster triage and resolution:\"}],\" Tenants are required to provide photos and select specific categories for maintenance up-front, allowing auto-dispatch algorithms to send the right contractor instantly.\"]}]\n2f:[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Higher tenant satisfaction:\"}],\" Modern renters, particularly Gen Z and Millennials, vastly prefer asynchronous, app-based communication over making phone calls during business hours.\"]}]\n30:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"financial\",\"children\":\"Automating financial reconciliation\"}]\n31:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If tenant communication is the biggest time drain, financial reconciliation is the biggest risk factor. Managing escrow accounts, separating operational funds, holding security deposits, and paying out owners accurately requires precision. When done manually on spreadsheets, the error rate is surprisingly high.\"}]\n32:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Scaling portfolios utilize bidirectional accounting integrations. When a tenant pays rent via the portal, the transaction should not just mark the invoice as \\\"paid.\\\" The system should automatically route the management fee to the agency account, route the remainder to the owner's account, and log the exact journal entry into QuickBooks or Xero without a human ever touching a keyboard.\",\" \",[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"blog-highlight-text\",\"children\":\"Firms utilizing this method process month-end close in 4 hours instead of 4 days.\"}]]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"case-study\",\"children\":\"Real-world case study: Elevate Properties\"}]\n34:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"To illustrate this, let's look at \",[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Elevate Properties\"}],\", a mid-sized agency managing 400 doors in the Midwest. In 2024, they employed 4 full-time property managers, maintaining an industry-standard 100:1 ratio. In early 2025, they acquired a massive new block of 300 doors. The leadership team initially planned to hire 3 new staff members to handle the load.\"]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"alt\":\"Data analysis showing growth and scaling metrics\",\"height\":620,\"src\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop\",\"width\":1200}]\n36:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Facing a tight labor market and shrinking margins, they decided to pause hiring. Instead, they spent 30 days migrating their disparate legacy systems into a single, unified cloud platform.\"}]\n37:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"By forcing 95% of their tenants onto auto-pay through the portal and utilizing AI-driven maintenance triaging to handle initial contractor dispatch, they successfully absorbed the 300 new doors without making a single operational hire.\"}]\n38:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Their door-to-manager ratio shifted from 100:1 to an impressive 175:1. This operational leverage massively increased their profit margins while actually improving their tenant satisfaction scores due to faster automated response times.\"}]\n39:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"conclusion\",\"children\":\"Conclusion & Next Steps\"}]\n3a:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Scaling your property portfolio does not have to mean scaling your payroll and dealing with the headaches of constant hiring and training. By auditing your team's current daily workflows, aggressively identifying repetitive manual tasks, and investing in a unified property management platform, you can unlock unprecedented growth.\"}]\n3b:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Your software should work for you, not the other way around. Ready to see how the right tools can help you achieve a 200:1 door-to-manager ratio while improving service quality?\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"#\",\"children\":\"Schedule a customized strategic demo with our team today\"}],\".\"]}]\n20:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n3d:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/05-c3ty_6dwfk.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n23:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"How to scale your property portfolio - NexSaS | Loglime\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Learn how property management teams can scale portfolio operations with automation, tenant self-service, and financial reconciliation workflows.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"robots\",\"content\":\"index, follow\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Loglime - Apps for Restaurants\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Restaurant app packages for digital menus, online ordering, bookings, loyalty and customer updates.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:url\",\"content\":\"http://localhost:3000\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:site_name\",\"content\":\"Loglime\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":\"og:type\",\"content\":\"website\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"8\",{\"name\":\"twitter:card\",\"content\":\"summary_large_image\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"9\",{\"name\":\"twitter:title\",\"content\":\"Loglime Restaurant Apps\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"10\",{\"name\":\"twitter:description\",\"content\":\"Apps for restaurants that want menus, orders, bookings and loyalty online.\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"11\",{\"rel\":\"shortcut icon\",\"href\":\"/brand/favicon.png\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"12\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/brand/favicon.png\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"13\",{\"rel\":\"apple-touch-ico